        <ontology:hasDescription>This VC is also present in othe MRLs such as Fuente Obejuna (14029), Alanís (41002), Cazalla de la Sierra (41032), Castillo de las Guardas (21031), Alájar (21001), Cumbres Mayores (21029), Encinasola (21031), Villaviciosa de Córdoba (14073).  </ontology:hasDescription>
